{"tid":1973113,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"【咁就失業】中國國腳多手塗改車牌片流出 廣州恒大炒魷重罰","createTime":"2020-04-15T03:43:48.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-15T06:57:03.000Z","uid":35562,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"27eefcb6c4d55eae132d2499b9922ee6aaf6773d","tid":1973113,"uid":35562,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-15T03:43:48.000Z","msg":"效力中超廣州恒大的國腳于漢超，早前在街上企圖塗改座駕的車牌被拍到，其後片段於網上流出。隨後廣州警方於微博表示于漢超將會就事件罰款5,000元兼扣12分，雖然公告其後被刪除，但周二晚上恆大發表聲明，將會開除于漢超。<br />\n<br />\n近日一段網上的短片中發現，恒大球員于漢超將座架泊在路邊，然後企圖將車牌上的「E」改成「F」。廣州交通警部門之後指于漢超已接受調查，並表示將罰款5,000元、行政拘留15日，兼扣12分。不過，奇怪的是公告在隨後忽然被刪。但晚上恒大發表公開聲明，指這位33歲的翼鋒違犯隊規「有任何違法犯罪行為者，開除」，決定開除于漢超。<br />\n<br />\n33歲的于漢超14年轉投恒大，助恒大贏得4次中超冠軍，以及15年的亞冠盃冠軍，但去季一直因傷缺陣，只為恒大上陣6場。而他亦是中國隊常客，去年年初的亞洲盃亦有份入選，中國傳媒估計中國足協或就今次事件追加處分停賽，或令其國家隊生涯同時完結。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.sports.appledaily.com/sports/20200415/YGTTMVDUABQHN6J3L5EA2DA54M/?utm_campaign=hkad_social_appledailysports&amp;utm_medium=social&amp;utm_source=facebook&amp;utm_content=link_post&amp;fbclid=IwAR1egl_n8AjZEt8JIcbGtCsX3DopqUmRa_BPkop5RyAf46E8jPPKUkPaVCE\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.sports.appledaily.com%2Fsports%2F20200415%2FYGTTMVDUABQHN6J3L5EA2DA54M%2F%3Futm_campaign%3Dhkad_social_appledailysports%26utm_medium%3Dsocial%26utm_source%3Dfacebook%26utm_content%3Dlink_post%26fbclid%3DIwAR1egl_n8AjZEt8JIcbGtCsX3DopqUmRa_BPkop5RyAf46E8jPPKUkPaVCE&d=kRIfmd%2Br1GQrfPRU1wEKQJwtdbXJE8TYY9MHUmPwwUI%3D&h=733aec1f\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.sports.appledaily.com%2Fsports%2F20200415%2FYGTTMVDUABQHN6J3L5EA2DA54M%2F%3Futm_campaign%3Dhkad_social_appledailysports%26utm_medium%3Dsocial%26utm_source%3Dfacebook%26utm_content%3Dlink_post%26fbclid%3DIwAR1egl_n8AjZEt8JIcbGtCsX3DopqUmRa_BPkop5RyAf46E8jPPKUkPaVCE&h=924fb649\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.sports.appledaily.com/sports/20200415/YGTTMVDUABQHN6J3L5EA2DA54M/?utm_campaign=hkad_social_appledailysports&amp;utm_medium=social&amp;utm_source=facebook&amp;ut